--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.19.0.1-3 (2020-01-07)
C: Rename project from btc_bitcoind to bitcoin_core

* Version 0.19.0.1-2 (2019-11-26)
E: Modify Dockerfile to support building with Podman

* Version 0.19.0.1-1 (2019-11-25)
C: Update bitcoin-core to version 0.19.0.1

* Version 0.18.1-2 (2019-11-18)
E: Update Docker image to CentOS 8

* Version 0.18.1-1 (2019-08-14)
C: Update bitcoin-core to version 0.18.1

* Version 0.18.0-1 (2019-05-08)
C: Update bitcoin-core to version 0.18.0
F: Add signature check for download

* Version 0.17.1-1 (2019-01-03)
C: Update bitcoin-core to version 0.17.1

* Version 0.17.0-1 (2018-11-23)
C: Update bitcoin-core to version 0.17.0

* Version 0.16.2-1 (2018-08-08)
F: Initial release
